WEBVTT

00:00.702 --> 00:01.902
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>The Borgias...</i>

00:01.970 --> 00:03.469
What of your
cardinals' fortunes?

00:03.504 --> 00:04.438
There were debts.

00:04.505 --> 00:05.705
The treasury is filling,

00:05.773 --> 00:07.674
but not to the extent
of equipping an army.

00:07.709 --> 00:09.676
Catherina Sforza gathers
allies to her daily -

00:09.711 --> 00:10.844
<i>like flies to a corpse.</i>

00:10.878 --> 00:12.446
<i>The ending will be war.</i>

00:12.480 --> 00:13.814
Well, what do you
expect me to do?

00:13.881 --> 00:15.148
Give me command!

00:15.283 --> 00:17.317
<i>A union</i>
<i>of Italian families.</i>

00:17.352 --> 00:19.152
<i>Together we would</i>
<i>be unbreakable.</i>

00:19.220 --> 00:20.621
Under you?
A woman?

00:20.655 --> 00:23.223
My hatred of the Borgia
Pope is public already.

00:23.291 --> 00:25.158
<i>Catherina Sforza's</i>
<i>son, Benito...</i>

00:25.193 --> 00:27.828
Remember this moment
as an act of mercy.

00:27.862 --> 00:29.663
<i>This dog</i>
<i>will come back and bite.</i>

00:29.697 --> 00:30.998
Let us raise our glasses,

00:31.032 --> 00:33.233
to this family that
we welcome as our own.

00:33.301 --> 00:35.502
I have a child who
must hear those words.

00:35.536 --> 00:38.005
We would welcome any
fruit of your union.

00:38.072 --> 00:40.173
All other fruit
is best forgotten.

00:40.241 --> 00:41.708
<i>Should I bring my child</i>

00:41.743 --> 00:43.543
<i>to this theatre of cruelty?</i>

00:43.611 --> 00:44.978
No!

00:45.013 --> 00:47.053
Well, as least now, my lady,
the choice is your own.

00:47.081 --> 00:49.483
Your Highness.

00:49.550 --> 00:51.852
This king desires
more than Naples.

00:51.886 --> 00:54.254
He has an equal
fondness for Milan.

00:54.355 --> 00:55.889
<i>You need a well-born bride.</i>

00:55.990 --> 00:57.190
The least of my needs.

00:57.258 --> 00:58.925
What I need most
of all, Cardinal,

00:58.993 --> 01:00.994
is an army that can
cut through Italy.

01:01.029 --> 01:02.496
What you propose

01:02.530 --> 01:05.732
could shake the foundations
of the Italian city states.

01:05.833 --> 01:07.701
But it would
give you Milan.

01:07.735 --> 01:09.703
And it would
give you an army.

01:11.673 --> 01:13.952
[♪]

